{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "report-service-comic-sans",
		"name": "Report Service — Comic Sans",
		"description": "# Report Service API Documentation\n\n## Overview\nThe **report-service** is a TypeScript microservice (port **3006**) that generates aggregated reports by calling other services via HTTP. It has **no database** of its own.\n\n## Architecture\n```\nHandler → HTTP Client → other services (no DB layer)\n```\n\n## Dependencies\n- **user-service** (port 3002) — for user listing\n- **customer-service** (port 3004) — for customer listing\n- **sales-service** (port 3005) — for sales by customer\n\n## Internal Access\nAll endpoints require `X-Internal: true` header.\n\n## Standard Response Envelope\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true | false,\n  \"data\": { ... } | null,\n  \"error\": null | \"Descriptive error message\"\n}\n```",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "base_url",
			"value": "http://localhost:3006",
			"type": "string",
			"description": "Base URL of the report-service (direct access)"
		},
		{
			"key": "gateway_url",
			"value": "http://localhost:8080",
			"type": "string",
			"description": "Base URL of the API Gateway (production entry point)"
		}
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Health Check",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Health Check",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/health",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["health"]
						},
						"description": "## Health Check\n\nReturns the health status of the report-service.\n\n### Authentication\nNone required.\n\n### Response\n- **200 OK** — Service is healthy"
					},
					"response": [
						{
							"name": "200 — Service Healthy",
							"originalRequest": {
								"method": "GET",
								"header": [],
								"url": {
									"raw": "{{base_url}}/health",
									"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
									"path": ["health"]
								}
							},
							"status": "OK",
							"code": 200,
							"_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
							"header": [
								{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json; charset=utf-8" }
							],
							"body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"service\": \"report-service\",\n    \"status\": \"ok\"\n  },\n  \"error\": null\n}"
						}
					]
				}
			],
			"description": "Service health and liveness probe."
		},
		{
			"name": "Reports",
