							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["users", "list"]
						},
						"description": "## List Users — Proxy (SP5-QA-01)\n\nProxy endpoint that forwards the request to user-service's `/users/list` and returns the response as-is.\n\n### Prerequisites\n- **user-service** must be running on port 3002\n\n### Response\n- **200 OK** — Array of users (same format as user-service)"
